{"tid":2347593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Twins明年成軍20周年 阿Sa阿嬌宣布2021年開騷","createTime":"2020-12-31T07:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:19:18.000Z","uid":133304,"like":6,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f3af13985531994aa60714d28d4ab33f9467952b","tid":2347593,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"本地女子組合Twins於2001年出道，明年正式成軍廿周年，近日鍾欣潼(阿嬌)出席活動時獲好姊妹蔡卓妍(阿Sa)驚喜隔空現身，以直播形式互動，期間兩人首度透露計劃明年舉行出道20周年演唱會！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZO28t7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZO28t7D.jpg&h=48e1a76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由蔡卓妍(阿Sa)和鍾欣潼(阿嬌)組成的Twins不經不覺邁向成軍20周年，她們出道即爆紅，是不少8、90後的青春偶像。雖然近年兩人經常分隔兩地工作，加上疫情緣故，令兩人聚少離多，但無礙姊妹感情。日前阿嬌出席代言活動時，阿Sa都特地以視像通話形式為阿嬌撐場，而阿嬌更現場演繹Twins代表作《下一站天后》，令粉絲回憶返晒嚟！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2021年是Twins成軍20周年，兩人趁機宣布計劃舉行慶祝出道20周年演唱會，事後，阿嬌在微博寫上：「20年仿佛一瞬間，一路上的坎坷不定但有你在身邊鼓勵，不管未來飛向何方，都會約定和你(蔡卓妍)&nbsp;一起20年後，再唱下一站天后。」<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/activity/detail/119534/twins%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%832021-twins%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E8%BB%8D20%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E9%98%BFsa%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%832021%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E9%A8%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Factivity%2Fdetail%2F119534%2Ftwins%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%25832021-twins%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25BB%258D20%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E9%2598%25BFsa%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25AC%258C%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%25832021%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A8%25B7&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=8844d9fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/activity/detail/119534/twins%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%832021-twins%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E8%BB%8D20%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E9%98%BFsa%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%832021%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E9%A8%B7</a>"},{"pid":"bf502a627aa09e3d4349ca9ca89bb6a3dc10b5e0","tid":2347593,"uid